# Goal Description

The goal is to build a complete, professional quality inspection flow within the mobile application. This includes a multi-field start screen, a dynamic checklist with conditional logic for defects (Yes/No/NA), and a comprehensive summary report screen.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The "Start Inspection" screen will now require 6 fields instead of 3. Ensure this aligns with the user's data requirements.

> [!NOTE]
> The checklist data will be extended to support `defectType` and `comment` fields only when "No" is selected.

